  "identifier": "HB 375",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to automated license plate readers.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 189 to define \"automated license plate reader\" or \"ALPR\"; prohibit the use, deployment, and maintenance of an ALPR system; allow a person to bring a civil action for a violation and allow recovery of actual and punitive damages; make the use, deployment, and maintenance of an ALPR system a Class D felony and set a fine of $10,000.",
